oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Red Cross notification of the death of Frank McClellan Ring
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph and documents sent by the Red Cross relating to the grave of Pvt. Frank McClellan Ring, Co. A, 114th MG BN, 117th Inf., 30th Div. consisting of a printed folder with photographs and hand written entry of the soldier's name, service, and grave location. The group also includes a cover letter and the original envelope.
